(x, y, -z) &= \left(2 \sin \left(\frac{8 \pi}{7}\right) \cos \left(\frac{2 \pi}{9}\right), 2 \sin \left(\frac{8 \pi}{7}\right) \sin \left(\frac{2 \pi}{9}\right), -2 \cos \left(\frac{8 \pi}{7}\right) \right),
\end{align*}where we used these to just obtain the expression
